{{!
    @template mod_simplelesson/summary_row
    Moodle table row rendering template for lesson attempt summary table.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * question string a question title
    * pagetitle string title of the page with the question
    * rightanswer string from the Moodle question table
    * youranswer string the student answer to the question
    * mark int the mark awarded for the answer
    * maxmark int the total mark available for the question
    * timetaken int the number of seconds taken in answering the question


    Example context (json):
        {
         "question": "Whether 'tis nobler...",
         "firstname": "Ford",
         "Lastname": "Prefect",
         "datetaken": "1970-1-1 12:00",
         "rightanswer": "In the mind",
         "youranswer": "In the arm",
         "mark": "1",
         "maxmark": "1",
         "timetaken": "42"
        }
}}
<tr class="danger">
  <td>{{question}}</td>
  <td>{{pagetitle}}</td>
  <td>{{right_answer}}</td>
  <td>{{{your_answer}}}</td>
  <td>{{mark}}</td>
  <td>{{maxmark}}</td>
  <td>{{timetaken}}</td>
</tr>
